headline: Panera Jumps Into Restaurant Discount Fight
summary: Panera Bread is wading into the restaurant industry’s value wars, and bringing its multi-million dollar ad budget. The fast-casual chain said Wednesday it will start selling a $4.99 mix-and-match deal, offering pairings of soups, salads and half sandwiches.
